# To get this token:
# 1. Go to Strapi Admin Panel (http://localhost:1337/admin)
# 2. Navigate to Settings → API Tokens
# 3. Click "Create new API Token"
# 4. Name it (e.g., "Frontend Token")
# 5. Token type: "Read-only" (or "Full access" if needed)
# 6. Copy the generated token and paste it below
